177 A.3d 118 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-CROSS-RESPONDENT, v. ANTHONY IRIZARRY A/K/A TONE, DEFENDANT-CROSS-PETITIONER.

C-423 September Term 2017

079684 December 8, 2017

ON CROSS PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A cross-petition for certification of the judgment in A-001518-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the cross-petition for certification is denied.
